h2. Watir 1.5

The "Users Guide":http://wiki.openqa.org/display/WTR/User+Guide provides an 
introduction to using Watir. 

The Watir Elements matrix provides an overview of the API.

Like other Ruby gems, Watir's API is documented with _rdoc._ To view the *Watir rdoc:* 
# Go to the Start menu, and select Ruby -> RubyGems -> Start RubyGems Rdoc Server. 
# Select Ruby -> RubyGems -> View Installed Gems Rdoc. 
# Select the Watir rdoc in the list that appears.

The "FAQ":http://wiki.openqa.org/display/WTR/FAQ provides answers to frequently 
asked questions.

* Several "Articles":http://wiki.openqa.org/display/WTR/Articles describe other aspects of Watir.

